Finally a nice way to have Zend Framework as a submodule
========================================================

To do this, follow these easy steps.

First, browse to your current git repository. Then execute this command:

    git submodule add git://github.com/komola/ZendFramework.git *your/path*

After that, navigate to the folder and execute:

    git checkout *the tagged version you'd like*

After that, you're done!
